Package com.idevicesinc.sweetblue.internal.android

Class AndroidBluetoothGatt

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.idevicesinc.sweetblue.internal.android.AndroidBluetoothGatt
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IBluetoothGatt
    public final class AndroidBluetoothGatt
extends java.lang.Object
implements IBluetoothGatt
    Default implementation of IBluetoothGatt, and wraps BluetoothGatt. This class is used by default by the library, and the only time it should NOT be used, is when unit testing.
    See Also:
    BleDeviceConfig.gattFactory
